{"tid":2143200,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"A-ha〈Take On Me〉三度發行終成代表作，經典MV破十億views！","createTime":"2020-08-07T03:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T11:00:57.000Z","uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"582ffec48ae30cabbd7d0babba74af766191f63c","tid":2143200,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/djV11Xbc914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdjV11Xbc914&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=c1309ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/djV11Xbc914</a><br />\n▲2019年末，A-ha〈Take On Me〉的MV已更新為4K修復版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自挪威奧斯陸的三人組合A-ha，是80年代的經典之一，成名曲〈Take On Me〉歷久不衰，近年仍有許多電影採用此曲作為配樂。而這首歌曲特殊的鉛筆動畫MV，在當年更是獲獎無數的經典視覺，近日也已在YouTube上獲得破十億觀看次數的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n1982年成立的經典synth-pop、新浪潮三人組合A-ha，由吉他手Paul Waaktaar-Savoy、鍵盤手Magne Furuholmen，以及主唱Morten Harket所組成。他們於80年代中期逐漸在歐美樂壇中崛起，並在90年代之後獲得全球性的商業成功，成為揚名國際的音樂團體。<br />\n<br />\n蔚為經典的A-ha的首支單曲〈Take on Me〉其實在1984年首度發行時，並未獲得廣大迴響；隔年A-ha推出首張錄音室專輯《Hunting High and Low》，換了製作人，重新錄製了新版〈Take on Me〉，以synth-pop為基礎，加入了木吉他、鍵盤、鼓組等各種樂器，成為大家最為熟知的版本，但成績上，仍沒有獲得太大起色；一直到A-ha第三次發行〈Take on Me〉，伴隨導演Steve Barron為歌曲拍攝具開創性的MV，將影像結合鉛筆素描、動畫、真人演出的轉描機技術（rotoscoping），讓〈Take on Me〉終於引起樂壇、媒體及樂迷們的注意，迅速登上歐美各大單曲榜，一舉拿下6項MTV音樂錄影帶的大獎。<br />\n<br />\n經過35年，A-ha在2019年年底獻上〈Take on Me〉的4K修復版MV，2月17日，在YouTube平台達成破10億次點閱次數的紀錄，成為繼Guns N&rsquo; Roses〈Sweet Child o&rsquo; Mine〉後第二首達標的80年代MV作品。從YouTube公布的數據顯示，自2020年起，〈Take On Me〉的每日觀看次數平均超過48萬次。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在近年音樂主題片的熱潮之下，A-ha宣布今年也要推出紀錄片《A-ha: The Movie》，內容由劇組團隊自2016年開始跟隨A-ha紀錄，以長達4年的經歷來闡述當年A-ha的成名故事，及他們近期在樂壇的動向與演變，預計11月26日將於世界各地首映，並且配合直播為樂迷們獻上獨家片段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ysolife.com/aha-take-on-me-mv-billion-streams/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fysolife.com%2Faha-take-on-me-mv-billion-streams%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=a8a8f272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ysolife.com/aha-take-on-me-mv-billion-streams/</a>"},{"pid":"d0a6da5884078edcb7e6859abbf07d64b5a91e89","tid":2143200,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"呢隊算唔算一曲走天涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三十幾年靠一首歌搵食"},{"pid":"f527ddedc7f9c96b41ef198e774cdcc65fc99c70","tid":2143200,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a6da5884078edcb7e6859abbf07d64b5a91e89","tid":2143200,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"呢隊算唔算一曲走天涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三十幾年靠一首歌搵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8b4b0d9fd82633f78989c806dc207c6ac57368","tid":2143200,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"第一次聽好似係玩sleeping dog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cfbc84917d516ddeeca59197b927afb170624d","tid":2143200,"uid":98242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"takkkkeeeee ooooonnnn mmmeee<br />\ntake on me<br />\ntakkeeeee meeeee onnnnnnn<br />\n<br />\nill be gone<br />\n in a day or twoooooooooooo"},{"pid":"612a78decfbb7c907cb5c5884059f4507f6f318f","tid":2143200,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺個士巴拿佬close up似成龍+Richard Hammond<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70e78ed2eea31cbd49334eab28500c1f42